#. type: Content of: <p>
#: doc/noosfero/plugins/shopping_cart.en.xhtml:27
msgid ""
"If you want to add new products just do the same thing. If you try to add a "
"product that&#8217;s already in your cart, it will add one to the quantity "
"of that product."
